title: Prosecutor facing possible impeachment submits resignation
description: FRANKFORT, Ky. (AP) — A Kentucky prosecutor facing possible impeachment over allegations that he promised a defendant favors in court in exchange for nude images of her has submitted his resignation. ...

title: Kentucky sees first infant anonymously surrendered at "baby box"
description: The child was dropped off in the last seven days at a safe-surrender "baby box" at a Bowling Green Fire Department and was picked up by department staff in less than 90 seconds.

title: Tourists are back and they're thirsty as the famous Kentucky Bourbon Trail shatters records with a 370% surge in attendance
description: Bourbon tourism in the state is booming with visits to distillers on the trail easily beating the pre-pandemic record of 1.7 million stops in 2019.
author: Bruce Schreiner, The Associated Press

title: KY schedules listening tour to gather input for internet broadband plan
description: Kentucky Gov. Andy Beshear said state officials have scheduled a six-week listening tour that will help officials identify which areas needs better internet access.
author: Associated Press

title: Kentucky Senate passes bill to ban TikTok from state-issued devices
description: The Kentucky Senate has passed a bill to ban the TikTok application from state-issued devices. This decision was made to protect the data on government devices.
author: Associated Press

title: KY prosecutor who is facing impeachment for offering favors in exchange for nude photos submits resignation
description: A prosecutor who is facing impeachment for promising favors in exchange for nude photos has submitted his resignation. The prosecutor's resignation will go into effect on Feb. 28.
author: Associated Press
